1. *Majicu* sam sinoć isprao. (I washed *the T-shirt* last night.)
2. Želim da kupim *majicu* u plavoj boji. (I want to buy *a T-shirt* in blue color.)
3. *Majicu* ti pozajmio nisam. (I didn't lend you *the T-shirt*.)
4. Ne volim da nosim *majicu* ispod košulje. (I don't like to wear *a T-shirt* under a shirt.)
5. Pogledaj ovu *majicu*, baš mi se sviđa dezen. (Look at this *T-shirt*, I really like the pattern.)
6. Na plaži nosim samo *majicu* i kupaće gaće. (I only wear *a T-shirt* and swimming trunks at the beach.)
7. *Majicu* koju si mi poklonio nosim svaki dan. (I wear the *T-shirt* you gave me every day.)
8. Ovo je nova *majica* koju sam kupio danas. (This is a new *T-shirt* I bought today.)
9. Stavi *majicu* u ormar. (Put *the T-shirt* in the closet.)
10. Nemoj da zaboraviš da opereš *majicu*. (Don't forget to wash *the T-shirt*.)